text:
Good; seems like a breakfast-only stall, because soya bean runs out after 11am+. Has bread, eggs, coffee, soya bean, grass jelly etc.

When ordering cold soya bean drink with ice, the uncle uses minimal ice so drink remains cold while maximising the amount of drink you get. Can also order without ice for the same price.
Teh was pretty good. Sellers were hygienic and friendly. Accepts e-payment too.
